Author: Synexcoin ICO
Title: Synexcoin ICO 48% of ICO revenue goes back to the investors!
Body: It looks like the softcap will not be reached ....   For this reason, we thank all ICO participants for the trust you have placed in us and we have a little surprise for all ICO participants!:   Each ICO participant receives a refund of his investment and he receives an additional 100% of his ICO investment back !!   In other words, anyone who has invested 1 ETH, for example, will receive 2 ETH back directly into his personal wallet.   We are already millionaires and would like to thank all of them for their trust in our project!   That is the reason for us to make this huge giveaway. It seems to have been the wrong time for our ICO, and as a result we will start a new project with a redesigned website in the future. !!! Synexcoin 2.0 !!!  Total Earned: 973,9989 ETH Total Tokens Sold: 1.284.930 Repayment to participants with 100% Bonus: 1875,9978 ETH  But now, unfortunately, we have to stop the project. Please beware of the scammers in the crypto-world and NEVER share your private keys or sensitive data with anyone in the chat!   The refund program will start immediately! Best regards and good luck, your Synexcoin-Team!!
